			</BitmapImage>
		</Group>
		<RichText x="1410" y="223" width="424" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">无相之火拳击地面，拳击后从内向外扩散出3道震波，锤击与震波均造成<span color="#ff9999">100%,50%,20%,10%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="671" width="424" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">无相之火朝向玩家并化成球滚动，造成<span color="#ff9999">80%</span><span>伤害；总共来回滚向玩家最多3次，接触造成</span><span color="#ff9999">50%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="895" width="439" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">无相之火包围核心，从「贯地千炎」技能留下的不灭熔口中升起3个<span textDecoration="underline">火种</span><span>，熄灭所有火种可中断其复燃进程。<br/>复燃成功后将恢复复燃值，其值遵循该式：</span><span color="#ff9999">27%+20%火种数量</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="671" width="427" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">无相之火移到场地中央，蜷缩成球状，8s后爆炸，造成<span color="#ff9999">250%</span><span>大范围伤害</span><span color="#ffbfbf">(闪避帧无效)</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/无相之火.assets/Image_14.png')" x="1391" y="137">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/无相之火.assets/Image_15.png')" x="719" y="585">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/无相之火.assets/Image_16.png')" x="1391" y="809">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/无相之火.assets/Image_17.png')" x="1391" y="586">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/无相之火.assets/Image_18.png')" x="720" y="362">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/无相之火.assets/Image_19.png')" x="1393" y="362">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/无相之火.assets/Image_20.png')" x="720" y="1065">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/无相之火.assets/Image_21.png')" x="1391" y="1066">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="738" y="447" width="424" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">无相之火化成蛇，向玩家喷出火球，喷球落地位置依次为玩家左、中、右处，每次喷3个火球，每个火球造成<span color="#ff9999">100%,50%,20%,10%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1409" y="447" width="438" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">无相之火依次变形呈成公牛、鲤鱼、蝴蝶进行攻击，公牛顶造成<span color="#ff9999">100%</span><span>伤害，鲤鱼跃出和跃入造成</span><span color="#ff9999">100%</span><span>伤害，出地爆炸造成</span><span color="#ff9999">100%</span><span>伤害，蝴蝶舞造成</span><span color="#ff9999">33%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="1151" width="439" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">无相之火开阵，8个火立方外壳围一圈暴露核心，一次性发射所有火立方追踪玩家，每个造成<span color="#ff9999">50%,25%,12.5%,5%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="1151" width="424" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">无相之火将外壳化为成两面墙，随后夹击，造成<span color="#ff9999">100%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="899" y="62" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#ad4218" width="207" height="28" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" color="#ad4218">制图@Csxylic米游社</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="66" y="1104" width="305" height="39" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">无殚焰胄：<span color="#ff9999">28火</span><span>盾，击破可熄灭无相之火。<br/>火种：</span><span color="#ff9999">2火</span><span>盾，全部击破阻止无相之火复燃。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="895" width="438" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">无相之火移到场地中央，暴露核心，不断产生炎柱，造成<span color="#ff9999">100%</span><span>伤害，炎柱在距离无相之火一定范围外会追踪玩家生成。首次升起3根炎柱，并留下3个不灭熔口。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/无相之火.assets/Image_22.png')" x="720" y="810">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/无相之火.assets/Image_23.png')" x="64" y="166" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/无相之火.assets/Image_24.png')" x="1268" y="171" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/无相之火.assets/Image_25.png')" x="1248" y="150" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="738" y="223" width="435" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">燃烧状态下的无相之火形成<span textDecoration="underline" color="#ff9999">无殚焰胄</span><span>，当复燃次数为</span><span color="#ff9999">1/2/&gt;2</span><span>时，无相之火每5s恢复</span><span color="#ff9999">5%/2.5%/0%</span><span>生命值，最大恢复至</span><span color="#ff9999">50%/25%/不恢复</span><span>生命值。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
